Sifter,is,a,bug,and,issue,tracking,platform,Sifter,provides,an,online,dashboard,for,teams,and,organizations,to,manage,and,track,bugs,and,issues,that,display,progress,people,working,on,the,bugs,and,issues,and,lists,all,issues,The,Sifter,API,allows,developers,to,access,the,data,and,functionality,of,Sifter,Currently,the,API,is,read,only,but,they,plan,on,making,write,access,available,as,well,The,current,API,method,is,searching,and,displaying,project,information